2019-03-08 11:56:06.228 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__waiterId_0='?' (Size = 450), @__start_1='?' (DbType = DateTime2), @__end_2='?' (DbType = DateTime2)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT DATEPART(year, [i].[DateCreated]) AS [c], DATEPART(month, [i].[DateCreated]) AS [c0], DATEPART(day, [i].[DateCreated]) AS [c1], [i.Customer].[TableCode], [i].[DateCreated]
FROM [Orders] AS [i]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [i.Customer] ON [i].[CustomerId] = [i.Customer].[Id]
